# AI-SDLC Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs)

## 🚀 **AI Governance | Risk Compliance | AI-IRB Standards**

This repository contains the **official Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs)** for the **AI-SDLC Institute**, governing **AI model compliance, risk assessment, and governance workflows**.

## 📖 **Repository Structure**
- 📜 `/sops/` – Core AI governance SOPs.
- 🖼️ `/diagrams/` – UML models for AI workflows.
- 🔄 `/workflows/` – AI-IRB & compliance approval processes.
- 📑 `/templates/` – AI governance & compliance templates.
- ✅ `/compliance/` – Self-certification & audit validation.
- 📊 `/reports/` – Generated AI governance reports.

## 📚 **How to Use**
1. **Browse SOPs** under `/sops/` for AI governance policies.
2. **Check AI workflows** in `/workflows/` for regulatory checkpoints.
3. **Validate compliance** using the self-certification checklist in `/compliance/`.
4. **Contribute** by submitting a pull request following [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md).

## 🔗 **Resources**
- 📜 **AI-SDLC Notion Knowledge Base**: [View Here](https://notion.ai-sdlc.institute)
- 🏛️ **Join AI Governance Discussions**: [Slack](https://join.slack.com/t/ai-sdlc/shared_invite/)
- 🎓 **Enroll in AI-IRB Certification**: [Courses](https://ai-sdlc.institute/membership)

