Directory Structure
Please maintain a well-structured repository by separating core SOPs, governance workflows, compliance validation, and supporting documents into clearly defined sections.

AI-SDLC-SOPs/
│── README.md                         # Overview & navigation guide
│── LICENSE                            # Open-source licensing (CC BY-SA 4.0)
│── CONTRIBUTING.md                    # Contribution guidelines
│── CODEOWNERS                         # Define required reviewers for compliance
│── .github/                           # GitHub automation & issue templates
│   ├── workflows/                     # Automated validation workflows
│   │   ├── validate-sops.yml
│   │   ├── generate-uml.yml
│── sops/                              # Official AI-SDLC SOPs (primary documents)
│   ├── SOP-0001-01-AI_Long-Friendly-Name.md
│   ├── SOP-0002-01-AI_Descriptive-and-Clear.md
│   ├── SOP-0003-01-AI_IRB-Gated-AI-SDLC-Institute.md
│   ├── index.md                       # Auto-generated SOP Table of Contents
│── diagrams/                          # UML diagrams & PlantUML source
│   ├── SOP-0001-01-AI.svg
│   ├── SOP-0001-01-AI.puml
│   ├── SOP-0001-02-AI.png
│── workflows/                         # Gated compliance workflows
│   ├── AI-IRB-Approval-Workflow.md
│   ├── AI-Governance-Checkpoints.md
│── templates/                         # Standardized templates for governance
│   ├── SOP-Template.md
│   ├── AI-IRB-Compliance-Checklist.md
│── compliance/                        # Self-certification & compliance validation
│   ├── Self-Certification-Checklist.md
│   ├── AI-Governance-Self-Audit.md
│── reports/                           # Generated reports for audits
│   ├── AI-Governance-Monthly-Report.pdf
│   ├── AI-SDLC-Compliance-Log.md
│── mkdocs.yml                         # Configuration for documentation site
